imi-kai-technologia/941060/oieaneu-proigoumenou-i-pagkosmia-meiosi-stis-genniseis-ta-kyria-aitia-tou-fainomenou" class=""><div data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="font-extrabold line-clamp-3 text-sm mb-1 cursor-pointer hover:text-primary duration-300 transition-all" _msttexthash="3717090" _msthash="499">UN: "Unprecedented" global decline in births - The main causes of the phenomenon</div></a><div data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="text-xs text-primary font-medium flex items-center gap-1 py-1"><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="498407" _msthash="500">Science and Technology...</span><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="11284" _msthash="501">|</span><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="30277" _msthash="502">20:15</span></div></article><hr data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="my-2 border-t border-gray-300"></div><div data-v-2e37b8b1=""><article data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="items-center px-3"><a data-v-2e37b8b1="" href="/politis-news/kosmos/941058/dytiki-oxthi-dekades-travmaties-se-epixeirisi-tou-israilinou-stratou-sti-namplous" class=""><div data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="font-extrabold line-clamp-3 text-sm mb-1 cursor-pointer hover:text-primary duration-300 transition-all" _msttexthash="2315079" _msthash="503">West Bank: Dozens injured in Israeli army operation in Nablus</div></a><div data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="text-xs text-primary font-medium flex items-center gap-1 py-1"><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="61139" _msthash="504">World</span><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="11284" _msthash="505">|</span><span data-v-2e37b8b1="" _msttexthash="31928" _msthash="506">19:57</span></div></article><hr data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="my-2 border-t border-gray-300"></div><div data-v-2e37b8b1=""><article data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="items-center px-3"><a data-v-2e37b8b1="" href="https://gipedo.politis.com.cy/omonoiaar/941057/anakoinothike-apo-ti-nea-tou-omada-o-satsias" rel="noopener noreferrer"><div data-v-2e37b8b1="" class="font-extrabold line-clamp-3 text-sm mb-1 cursor-pointer hover:text-primary duration-